data.description: 2.5 acres of spacious country living and modern comforts, boasting a 4-bed, 2-bath mobile home that's ready to become your dream residence. This charming home offers a spacious and comfortable layout with a living room, family room off of the kitchen and additional sitting area in the primary bedroom. Property has a horseshoe driveway, multiple storage buildings, carports, covered front and back porches, 600' well and septic system. Property has electric and water all the way to the back. You can enjoy the serenity of country living while remaining well-connected to modern amenities, local attractions and essential services.  Whether you're seeking a serene retreat, a spacious environment for your family, or a canvas for your outdoor aspirations, this property holds the potential to make your dreams a reality. Schedule a showing today and take the first step toward embracing the limitless possibilities that await you in this remarkable piece of land. County taxes and SFISD!
